SUMMARY:Open House
DESCRIPTION:Splat Space - Durham's Hackerspace\nEvery Saturday between 1pm
  to 4pm we open our doors to the public to give anyone who wants to stop b
 y a chance to see our space. It's a chance for prospective new members to 
 take a tour of our space and ask any questions they have about what we off
 er.\n\nFeel free to come by or contact us if you want to schedule a tour.
