BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Splat Space (Durham Hackerspace)
UID:event_313858183@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260403T030127Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260408T170000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260408T200000
SUMMARY:Woodshop Wednesdays
DESCRIPTION:Splat Space - Durham's Hackerspace\nWhat is Wood-shop Wednesda
 y? Well its basically an open house for the Splat Space Wood-shop.\n\nHave
  a project you need help with? Want to learn how to safely use the wood sh
 op equipment? Just want to hang out and talk shop? Come on by. Each week o
 ne or more of our more knowledgeable wood workers will be there to help. N
 o need to sign up.\n\nNot a Splat Space member?\nWell you are also welcome
  to join us\, but unfortunately because of insurance limitation\, you cann
 ot use the equipment.\n\nWe look forward to seeing you all there!
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/splatspace/events/313858183/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260319T222532Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260319T222532Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
